  "title": "Core Concepts of Sex Education",
  "lessonText": "Understanding the fundamentals of sex education is essential for informed decision-making.",
  "data": {
    "content": "- Sex education encompasses a range of topics including anatomy, consent, relationships, and sexual health.\n- It aims to provide individuals with knowledge to make safe and healthy choices.\n- Key concepts include understanding one's own body, respecting boundaries, and recognizing healthy versus unhealthy relationships.\n- Comprehensive sex education promotes open dialogue and reduces stigma around sexual topics."
  }
}
